data.description: This charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers both comfort and charm. Step inside to discover a freshly painted interior that exudes warmth throughout. This two-story residence boasts ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The main level features a cozy library, providing a serene retreat from the bustle of daily life. The kitchen provides amble space for storage with tons of counter space and cabinets w/ an additional area for a desk/coffee bar! For convenience, it is open concept to the family room! Upstairs, retreat to the primary suite w/ a large walk-in closet, complete with a private ensuite bathroom featuring dual sinks and a soaking tub. Three additional bedrooms offer versatility and comfort for family and guests, while a shared full bathroom ensures convenience for all. Laundry is made easy with the room being oversized and upstairs. Perfect for additional storage too! Step outside to the expansive back deck, where outdoor gatherings await. The fenced backyard is perfect for your furry friends. Conveniently located in a quiet cul-de-sac and near schools, parks, and golf courses, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this beautiful property yours - schedule a showing today.
